The error in this program is due to trying to add a `String` (profile.score
(profile.scoreText) with an `Number` (raw.bonus). In Tundra, you can't dire
directly concatenate two different types together like this. The fix will i
involve converting the scoreText into a number before adding it to the bonu
bonus.

Here is the corrected program:

```tundra
val raw = {
  user: {
    score: 12,
    scores: [10, 11, 12],
    scoreText: "12"
   },
  bonus: 3
};

val profile = raw.user;
// Convert the String into Number using parseNumber function
val total = parseNumber(profile.scoreText) + raw.bonus;
print(total);
```
